
A Bitcoin mining pool using the hopper-proof PPLNS payout scheme.

* Offers full 8 decimal precision payouts
* Mining on port 80 if you're behind a firewall
* SSL
* Long Polling

##Reward distribution

* PPLNS: 0% fee, transaction fees distributed to miners.

